title: The Chattanooga Cheug Cheug 9/2: Joe Rogan, Supreme Court, Adult Swim, Joe Manchin, Candice Owens, Extreme Weather

description:
In this edition of The Chattanooga Cheug Cheug, Jack and Miles discuss Joe Rogan getting COVID, the Supreme Court letting the Texas abortion ban ride, Adult Swim turning 20, Joe Manchin opposing $3.5 trillion infrastructure bill, Candice Owens being denied service at a COVID test site for spreading misinformation, and US leadership doing nothing in the face of extreme weather
